<LI><STRONG>Innovations 2005 honorees</STRONG> and <STRONG>Best of Innovations</STRONG> product displays </LI>
<LI><STRONG>New to market</STRONG> exhibits, featuring examples of how to effectively introduce new products to market </LI>
<LI><STRONG>Design Company Displays</STRONG>, highlighting design capabilities from members of the IDSA </LI>
