<P>Innovations Plus is open to International CES exhibitors, companies with new products, releases or versions, Innovations 2005 honorees and entrants, and participants in CES Unveiled: The Official Press Event of the International CES. </P>For more information, contact an International CES representative at (703) 907-7645.
